Dana Wheeler-Nicholson https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dana_Wheeler-Nicholson 0 Dana Wheeler-Nicholson (born October 9, 1960) is an American actress and singer best known for her roles in the films Fletch (1985), Tombstone (1993), Fast Food Nation (2006) and Parkland (2013). She is also known for her roles on television series such as Friday Night Lights, and Nashville.
